---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Container } from "@/components/layout/Container";
import HeroImage from "../components/ui/HeroImage.astro";
import { ArrowRight } from "lucide-react";
---

<Layout
    title="Daycare Business Plan | Childcare Business Plan"
    description="Your daycare business plan needs accurate financial projections based on your state's regulations and local market conditions."
>
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <HeroImage
                src="/images/startup/daycare-business-plan.webp"
                alt="Visual breakdown of a professional Daycare Business Plan showing financial projections and growth milestones"
                className="mb-4 md:mb-12"
            />
            <div class="text-center">
                <span class="pro-text-meta mb-2 block">
                    Business Planning
                </span>
                <h1 class="text-xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6">
                    YOUR Business Plan
                </h1>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                    A business plan is only as good as the numbers behind it. Generic templates can't account for your state's regulations or local market rates.
                </p>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- FACTORS SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section bg-gray-50/50">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card mb-3 md:mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">
                    What Affects Your Projections
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    <p>
                        Financial projections are the heart of any plan. Your state determines your maximum capacity, which caps your revenue. Your local market determines what rates parents will pay, which drives your income per child.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        A home daycare might require minimal modifications or extensive health/safety renovations. A center faces completely different compliance costs that vary by state and municipality.
                    </p>
                    <p class="hidden md:block">
                        Beyond costs, your plan needs to account for realistic enrollment curves, seasonal attendance patterns, and the competitive landscape.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- WHY GENERIC FAILS SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">
                    Why Templates Fail
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    <p>
                        Templates use placeholder numbers that might be completely wrong for you. Fill-in-the-blank projections can't account for the specific regulatory constraints that define actual performance.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Investors and lenders want projections grounded in your specific opportunity. A business plan built on generic assumptions could lead to catastrophic planning errors.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card text-center border-2 border-teal-200/50 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50/20 to-white/50">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-4">
                    See Real Revenue Potential
                </h2>
                <p class="text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 mb-3 md:mb-6">
                    Start your business plan with accurate income projections based on your state's regulations.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="/#calculator"
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white font-bold px-5 py-2 md:px-8 md:py-4 shadow-lg transition-all text-xs md:text-base group"
                >
                    Use the Free Calculator
                    <ArrowRight className="w-3.5 h-3.5 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" />
                </a>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>
</Layout>
